title: The 350 HP VCMC Turbo Scion FR-S - /TUNED
description: Tuned heads to Chuckwalla Raceway to test out VCMC's Turbo FR-S, built for Canada's Tuner Challenge. It's a fully built track car, and as an added challenge, Matt gets to share the track with the practice session for the 24 Hours of Lemons.
